---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="bg-gray-800 text-white mt-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left border-b border-gray-700 pb-6 mb-6">

            <div class="md:w-1/3 mb-4 md:mb-0">
                <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-indigo-400">Marcos: Alma de Niño & Capitán</h4>
